&lt;li&gt;Proven experience in a similar commercial role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;History of consistently reaching targets in a similar capacity over the past few years&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience with subscription-based, renewal license models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to build and maintain trusted relationships with multiple stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professional communication and negotiation skills&lt;/li&gt;
