&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;At Trustpilot, we&#39;re on an incredible journey. We&#39;re a profitable, high-growth FTSE-250 company with a big vision: to become the universal symbol of trust. We run the world&#39;s largest open customer review platform, and while we&#39;ve come a long way, there&#39;s still so much exciting work to do. Come join us at the heart of trust!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pointer-events-none h-px w-px&quot; data-edge=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
