&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate about AI and how it changes the way people work. You have hands-on experience driving AI adoption and digital transformation. You understand the technology, but more importantly, you understand people and how to bring them on the journey.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strategic architect, not just a programme manager. You build systems and frameworks that create lasting change. You have a track record of designing

