&lt;li&gt;Act as the first line for customer issues related to onboarding, usage, or product value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Marketing to identify case study, testimonial, and reference opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Product to share structured customer feedback and insights that inform roadmap improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate health metrics, notes, and success plans in CRM for full portfolio visibility.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
